# The published site is intentionally minimal. Ignore EVERYTHING, then
# allow-list only the files that belong on vivekbansal.com. This is a safety
# net so local working material (notes/, gallery/, versions/, img/, configs
# with personal prompts) can never be committed by an accidental `git add -A`.
/*

!index.html
!archive.html
!about.html
!CNAME
!.nojekyll
!.gitignore
